<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وبَدِغَتِ <span class="c2">(٦٣)</span> الناقَةُ: أي سَمِنَتْ فَثَقُلَتْ <span class="c2">(٦٤)</span>.<span class="c5"> والبَدَغُ:</span> السِّمَنُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">والبَدْغُ:</span> الخَرْءُ، وهو بَدِغٌ بخرئه.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
