<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>الدَّبْغُ <span class="c2">(٦٥)</span>: مَصْدَرُ قَولِكَ دَبَغْتُ الجِلْدَ.<span class="c5"> والدِّبَاغُ:</span> الاسْمُ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
